title: Crowd Gathers Outside Ohio Statehouse to Protest Coronavirus Lockdown
description: A large number of protesters gathered outside the Ohio Statehouse again on Monday to make their voices heard during the press conference held by Gov. Mike DeWine, Lt. Gov. Jon Husted, and Ohio Department of Health Director Dr. Amy Acton.
